beer.beer_description:
Duel takes hops to the next level. With an interesting hop finish, this brew has a subtle floral & lightly spiced flavours with rich tropical fruit & citrus aromas. This brew has a full mouth feel, bright nose & a crisp finish. 
Brewed from Australian Pilsner malt and a touch of German Dextrin malt, this lager is refreshing in flavour, clean & crisp with an interesting hop combination of Summer, Ella and US Cascade & Citra. 
Duel is best served with a roast dinner, chicken & leafy greens. The hoppiness of this brew pairs perfectly with spicy food, pizza & light seafood.
